~ start
I’ve been making games since I was in middle school, though what I was making at that time could barely be called “games”.
The most I did was play around in a copy of RPGMaker VX Ace that most definitely wasn’t obtained through legal means.
I own like three versions of RPGMaker on Steam legally now, but my fondest memories are still back in those days,
where I made random bosses and drew a bunch of random maps and fumbled around without any care in the world.
